uy-Trinh/T%E1%BB%A5c-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BB%8B-ph%E1%BB%A5/poem-t7x3D5_IDRVJVwLZo-9BUw">Tục đề Vương thị phụ - 續題王氏婦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy-Trinh/author-tbuJ74IPkvZZ32WHu1yvJw">Dương Duy Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Trinh-B%E1%BA%A1ch/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-phi-o%C3%A1n/poem-ZPH8rLOxa4-PpUwHBOyG1Q">Tương phi oán - 湘妃怨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Trinh-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-4YLkec_RIGStgOJUrV0OuQ">Vương Trinh Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BB%B3-b%C3%A0-h%C3%A0nh/poem-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Tỳ bà hành - 琵琶行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br></div>	</div>
